data.description: Two Story 4 bedroom, very close to play park. Detailed tiled entry way flows into the formal living Room with bright windows. Kitchen has granite counter tops includes island with cabinets, pantry, range, microwave & double door refrigerator. Breakfast/Dining Room which flows into the fun family room which has access to large grassy backyard. Upstairs is a lovely large loft in the middle of all the bedrooms. Double Car Garage and Refrigerated Air complete this amazing home.
